<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
<body>
<p>Hi {{.Name}},</p>
{{- if eq .ThresholdDays 0}}
<p>A maintenance task on <strong>{{.CommodityName}}</strong> is now <strong>overdue</strong>.</p>
{{- else}}
<p>This is your <strong>{{.ThresholdDays}}-day maintenance reminder</strong>
for <strong>{{.CommodityName}}</strong>.</p>
{{- end}}
<p>Task: <strong>{{.MaintenanceTitle}}</strong><br/>
Due: <strong>{{.MaintenanceDueDate}}</strong></p>
{{- if .CommodityURL}}
<p>You can review the item here: <a href="{{.CommodityURL}}">{{.CommodityURL}}</a></p>
{{- end}}
<p>Inventario sends this so you can plan the maintenance before it
slips further past due.</p>
</body>
</html>
